Cilmi baarista aan caadiga ahayn: Heerka borotiinka C-reactive (CRP) ee dhiigga ayaa ka tarjumaya halista caabuqa ama dhaawaca unugyada waxaana la soo jeediyay in ay tahay arrin laga yaabo inay ku hormariso cudurka, jawaabta daaweynta, iyo soo kabashada ugu dambeysa.
Isku xirnaanta heerka CRP ee halista iyo saadaasha COVID-19 ayaa sidoo kale la soo jeediyay.
Intaa waxaa dheer, heerarka sare ee lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), iyo creatine kinase (CK) ayaa sidoo kale ka caawin kara saadaalinta natiijada.
Enzymes-yadaas waxaa si weyn loogu muujiyaa xubno badan, gaar ahaan wadnaha iyo beerka, waxaana la sii daayaa marka uu unuggu dhaco.
Sidaa darteed, waxay calaamadeyn caadi ah u yihiin qalbiga ama qalliinka beerka.
Calaamadaha waaweyn ee bukaanka: Sawirada laabta iyo horumarka waqtiga ee calaamadaha bukaanka waa in lagu tixgeliyaa marka la eego arrimaha kale ee saadaalinta natiijooyinka iyo dhibaatooyinka COVID-19.
Isticmaalka steroids: Sida kor lagu sharaxay, steroids waa daawooyinka difaaca jirka ee sida caadiga ah loo isticmaalo daaweynta dheeraadka ah ee cudurada faafa si loo yareeyo halista dhaawaca caabuqa.
