Ugu dambeyntii, dhoofinta alaabada ka imanaya aagagga juqraafi ahaan ay si weyn u saameysay COVID-19 ayaa la joojin karaa. Qorshaha diyaarinta cudurka faafa iyo jawaabta ayaa loo isticmaali karaa si loo hagaajiyo tallaabooyinka ilaalinta.
