Shaqooyinka halista sare leh waxaa ka mid ah bixinta daryeelka caafimaadka, taageerada, shaybaarka, iyo shaqaalaha gaadiidka caafimaadka ee la kulma bukaannada la yaqaan ama loo maleynayo inay qabaan COVID-19.
Kuwani waxay noqdaan khatar aad u sarreysa haddii shaqaaluhu sameeyaan hababka abuuraya aerosol, ama ay ururiyaan ama gacanta ku hayaan shaybaarada bukaannada la yaqaan ama loo maleynayo inay qabaan COVID-19.
Nidaamyada soo saara aerosol waxaa ka mid ah intubation, nidaamyada soo jiidashada qufaca, bronchoscopy, qaar ka mid ah nidaamyada ilkaha iyo baaritaannada, ama qaadashada shaybaarka.
Shaqooyinka xafiiska meydka ee halista sare leh waxaa ka mid ah shaqaalaha ku lug leh diyaarinta meydka dadka la ogyahay ama loo shakiyay inay qabaan COVID-19 waqtiga ay dhinteen; kuwani waxay noqdaan halis aad u sarreeya oo soo-gaadhsiinta ah haddii ay sameeyaan baaritaan meydka. Xakamaynta injineernimada ee dheeraadka ah ee kooxahan halista ah waxaa ka mid ah qolalka go'doominta ee bukaannada la yaqaan ama loo shakiyo COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan marka la sameeyo nidaamyada abuuraya aerosol.
Hawo-qaadista cadaadiska diidmada ah ee khaaska ah ayaa ku habboon daryeelka caafimaadka iyo meelaha meydka lagu aaso.
