Talaalka murashaxa ah ayaa lagu baaray shaybaar, iyadoo tijaabooyinka aadanaha la qorsheeyay bisha Luulyo ama Agoosto 2020.
Horraantii toddobaadkan, The Guardian ayaa soo warisay in Madaxweynaha Mareykanka Donald Trump uu CureVac u soo bandhigay "'lacag aad u badan' si uu u helo tallaalka COVID-19", taas oo dowladda Jarmalku ka soo horjeeddo.
