Talyaaniga 17 Maarso 2020, Takis Biotech, oo ah shirkad Talyaani ah oo tiknoolajiyada noolaha ah ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay yeelan doonaan natiijooyinka baaritaanka ka hor inta aan la gaarin April 2020 iyo in murashaxa ugu dambeeya ee tallaalkooda uu bilaabi karo tijaabinta aadanaha xilliga dayrta.
